## Cramp Prevention — Key Habits Throughout

- Drink **500ml electrolyte drink** in the 2 hours before every long session
- During sessions over 90 min, take **electrolytes every 30–40 min** (not just water)
- The poolside leg exercises (squats, lunges, calf raises) directly target cramp prevention by activating legs under swim fatigue
- Add **extra salt to meals** in the final 10 days
- In long sessions, practice eating race-day nutrition (the race uses Umara gels/bars)

